{"id":13910,"date":"2013-05-02T14:36:13","date_gmt":"2013-05-02T10:36:13","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=13910"},"modified":"2019-04-30T10:41:25","modified_gmt":"2019-04-30T06:41:25","slug":"life-do-not-kill-tawhid","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/life-do-not-kill-tawhid\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Life: No killing disbelievers if they claim to accept Islam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Miqdad ibn al-Aswad reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, if I confront an unbeliever and we fight each other and he severs one of my hands with his sword, then he hides from me behind a tree and claims he has submitted himself to Allah, should I kill him?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Do not kill him<\/b>.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, he cut off one of my hands and only then he said it!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Do not kill him. If you do so, he will be in your position before you killed him, and you will be in his position before he said it<\/b>.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3794, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 95<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/strong><\/em> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0642\u0650\u064a\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0641\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631\u0650 \u0641\u